option_c_hi":"1 और 2 दोनों","option_d_hi":"न तो 1 और न ही 2"},{"id":773,"quiz_id":59,"topic_id":1012,"sort_order":3,"question":"Assertion (A): Aurangzeb's long campaign in the Deccan ultimately led to the financial and military exhaustion of the Mughal Empire.\\n\\nReason (R): He successfully annexed the Sultanates of Bijapur and Golconda but completely failed to suppress the Maratha resistance.\\n\\nCodes:","question_hi":"अभिकथन (A): दक्कन में औरंगज़ेब के लंबे अभियान के परिणामस्वरूप अंततः मुग़ल साम्राज्य का वित्तीय और सैन्य पतन हुआ।\\n\\nकारण (R): उसने बीजापुर और गोलकुंडा के सल्तनतों को सफलतापूर्वक जीत लिया, लेकिन मराठा प्रतिरोध को दबाने में पूरी तरह विफल रहा।\\n\\nकूट:","option_a":"Both A and R are true and R explains A","option_b":"Both A and R are true but R does not explain A","option_c":"A is true but R is false","option_d":"A is false but R is true","option_a_hi":"A और R दोनों सत्य हैं तथा R, A की सही व्याख्या करता है","option_b_hi":"A और R दोनों सत्य हैं लेकिन R, A की सही व्याख्या नहीं करता है","option_c_hi":"A सत्य है लेकिन R असत्य है","option_d_hi":"A असत्य है लेकिन R सत्य है"},{"id":774,"quiz_id":59,"topic_id":1012,"sort_order":4,"question":"By which of the following titles was Mughal Emperor Aurangzeb widely known among his contemporary chroniclers due to his simple and orthodox lifestyle?","question_hi":"अपने सादे और कट्टरपंथी जीवन शैली के कारण मुग़ल सम्राट औरंगज़ेब अपने समकालीन इतिहासकारों के बीच निम्नलिखित में से किस उपाधि से व्यापक रूप से जाना जाता था?","option_a":"Shah-i-Bekhabar","option_b":"Zinda Pir","option_c":"Sahib-i-Qiran","option_d":"Sikandar-i-Sani","option_a_hi":"शाह-ए-बेखबर","option_b_hi":"ज़िंदा पीर","option_c_hi":"साहिब-ए-किरान","option_d_hi":"सिकंदर-ए-सानी"},{"id":775,"quiz_id":59,"topic_id":1012,"sort_order":5,"question":"Match the following rebellions during Aurangzeb's reign with their associated leaders/regions:\\n\\nList-I\\n(a) Jat Rebellion\\n(b) Bundela Rebellion\\n(c) Marwar Rebellion\\n(d) Satnami Rebellion\\n\\nList-II\\n(i)